quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,94,keh do ke agar akhirat ka ghar aur logon ( yani musalmanoon ) ke liye nahi aur khuda ke nazdeek tumahray hi liye makhsoos hai to agar sachey ho to mout ki arzoo to karo
  2,95,"lekin un aamaal ki wajah se, jo un ke haath agay bhaij chuke hain, yeh kabhi is ki arzoo nahi karen ge, aur khuda zaalmon se ( khoob ) waaqif hai"
  2,96,"balkay un ko tum aur logon se zindagi ke kahin harees dekho ge, yahan taq ke mushrikon se bhi. un mein se har aik yahi khwahish karta hai ke kash woh hazaar baras jeeta rahay, magar itni lambi Umar is ko mil bhi jaye to usay azaab se to nahi churra sakti. aur jo kaam yeh karte hain, khuda un ko dekh raha hai"
  2,97,"keh do ke jo shakhs jbryil ka dushman ho ( is ko ghusse mein mar jana chahiye ) is ne to ( yeh kitaab ) khuda ke hukum se tumahray dil par nazil ki hai jo pehli kitabon ki tasdeeq karti hai, aur imaan walon ke liye hadaayat aur basharat hai"
  2,98,jo shakhs khuda ka aur is ke firshton ka aur is ke payghambaroon ka aur jbryil aur mikaeel ka dushman ho to aisay kafiroon ka khuda dushman hai
  2,99,"aur hum ne tumahray paas suljhi hui ayatain arsaal farmai hain, aur un se inkaar wohi karte hain jo badkaar hain"
  2,100,un logon ne jab ( khuda se ) ehad wasiqkiya to un mein se aik fareeq ne is ko ( kisi cheez ki terhan ) pheink diya. haqeeqat yeh hai ke un mein aksar be imaan hain
  2,101,"aur jab un ke paas allah ki taraf se paighambar ( aakhir uz zamaan ) aeye, aur woh un ki ( aasmani ) kitaab ki bhi tasdeeq karte hain to jin logon ko kitaab di gayi thi, un mein se aik jamaat ne khuda ki kitaab ko peeth peechay pheink diya, goya woh jantay hi nahi"
